A simple Java application demonstrating Spring Framework Dependency Injection (DI) using XML-based configuration.

This project demonstrates:
Creating a Java application using Spring Tool Suite (STS)
Configuring Spring using applicationContext.xml
Creating and managing Spring Beans
Injecting object properties using XML configuration
Retrieving beans from the Spring IoC Container

# 🌱 Spring Framework XML Configuration Demo

> A beginner-friendly Java project demonstrating Dependency Injection (DI) using Spring Framework XML Configuration.

